title: ThisDot JS Marathon: End-to-end Testing with Cypress
description: Looking to add testing to your skill set or just feel more confident pushing to production? In this beginner-level talk, we will walk through the process of installing, configuring, and writing a critical-path test using Cypress.

title: Ioniconf 2020: End-to-end Testing Mobile Apps with Ionic and Cypress
description: JavaScript for mobile development AND testing? With Ionic and Cypress, developers can leverage frameworks they already love to code and test PWA and mobile applications prior to native complication.

title: Coders Craft Dev Meetup: The Road to Junior Dev - What and How to Learn
description: A discussion and QA with the Coders Craft Dev Meetup on what and how to learn on your journey into tech.

title: Node.js and Github API to Increase Productivity
description: More than 40 million developers use GitHub to store, share, and collaborate on open-source software. Learn how to leverage its robust API with lightweight Node scripts to increase productivity in your individual or team development process. Automate issues, release notes, and more!

title: Navigating a New Codebase: Tips and Tricks to Ease the Transition
description: A webinar for Women Who Code Front End about my transition from boot camp student to junior software developer.
